body_html:
0.11 is a very old release (prior to stability guarantees of 1.0). Is it possible for you to use 1.0?

That said, please provide all information asked for in the new issue template. Without that it is hard to be able to help (in particular, do provide the exact sequence of commands to reproduce the problem).

Thanks!
